<subSubSection pageId="21" pageNumber="22" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1436,576,1033]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,265,577,601]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Remarks.</emphasis>
There has been historic confusion over the authority for this genus (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation author="Sieg" box="[1062,1183,577,601]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Sieg, J. (1983) Tanaidacea. In Gruner, H. E. &amp; Holthuis, L. B. (Eds), Crustaceorum Catalogus. W. Junk, Belgium, 6, 1 - 552." type="journal article" year="1983">
Sieg, 
<number box="[1124,1183,577,601]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1983.0">1983</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[1193,1293,577,601]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="108.5" valueMax="109.0" valueMin="108.0">108–109</number>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Gutu" box="[1304,1432,576,601]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Gutu, M. (1980) Pseudosphyrapus, a new genus of a new family (Sphyrapidae) of Monokophora (Crustacea, Tanaidacea). Travaux du Museum d'Histoire naturelle &quot; Grigore Antipa &quot;, 22, 393 - 400." type="journal article" year="1980">
Guţu, 
<number box="[1373,1432,577,601]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1980.0">1980</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[151,195,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="393.0">393</number>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Larsen" box="[208,356,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Larsen, K. (2005) Deep-sea Tanaidacea (Peracarida) from the Gulf of Mexico. Crustacean Monographs, 5, 1 - 381." type="journal article" year="2005">
Larsen, 
<number box="[297,356,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="2005.0">2005</number>
</bibRefCitation>
: 
<number box="[368,399,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="77.0">77</number>
), but, as 
<bibRefCitation author="Sars" box="[500,672,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Sars, G. O. (1882) Revision af gruppen: Isopoda Chelifera med charakteristik af nye herhen horende arter og slaegter. Archiv for Mathematik og Naturvidenskab, 7 (1), 1 - 54." type="journal article" year="1882">
Sars (
<number box="[563,623,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1882.0">1882</number>
: 
<number box="[635,663,613,637]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="18.0">18</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
clearly designates it as “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Norman M.S." authorityName="Norman M.S." box="[950,1226,613,637]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[950,1066,613,637]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus</emphasis>
Norman M.S.
</taxonomicName>
” (“M.S.” meaning “manuscript”, not the initials of Alfred Merle Norman), then under Article 
<number box="[988,1043,649,673]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="50.1">50.1</number>
. 
<number box="[1047,1057,649,673]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1.0">1</number>
of the International Code of Zoological Nomenclature (
<collectionCode box="[402,472,685,709]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">ICZN</collectionCode>
), the authority is Norman, 
<number box="[766,821,685,709]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1882.0">1882</number>
(or “Norman in Sieg, 
<number box="[1066,1126,685,709]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1882.0">1882</number>
”).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1436,576,1033]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
Conversely, while Sars (
<emphasis box="[476,520,721,745]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">ibid</emphasis>
.) listed four named species (including “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Norman M.S." authorityName="Norman M.S." box="[976,1375,721,745]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malleolus">
<emphasis box="[976,1212,721,745]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus malleolus</emphasis>
Norman M.S.
</taxonomicName>
” and “ 
<taxonomicName authority="Norman M.S." authorityName="Norman M.S." box="[163,515,757,781]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tudes">
<emphasis box="[163,349,757,781]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus tudes</emphasis>
Norman M.S.
</taxonomicName>
”: 
<bibRefCitation author="Sars" box="[540,656,757,781]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Sars, G. O. (1882) Revision af gruppen: Isopoda Chelifera med charakteristik af nye herhen horende arter og slaegter. Archiv for Mathematik og Naturvidenskab, 7 (1), 1 - 54." type="journal article" year="1882">
Sars 
<number box="[597,656,757,781]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1882.0">1882</number>
</bibRefCitation>
, p. 
<number box="[698,729,757,781]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="20.0">20</number>
), he did not designate a type-species. As Sars’ publications of 
<taxonomicName box="[151,288,793,817]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malleolus">
<emphasis box="[151,288,793,817]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. malleolus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[342,429,793,817]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tudes">
<emphasis box="[342,429,793,817]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. tudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
did not meet the criteria of Article 
<number box="[826,854,793,817]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="12.0">12</number>
of the 
<collectionCode box="[933,1001,793,817]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">ICZN</collectionCode>
, each of the names as used in the 
<number box="[1380,1436,793,817]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1882.0">1882</number>
publication becomes a 
<emphasis box="[408,566,829,853]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">nomen nudum</emphasis>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Norman" box="[580,888,829,853]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Norman, A. M. &amp; Stebbing, T. R. R. (1886) On the Crustacea Isopoda of the ' Lightning ', ' Porcupine ' and ' Valorous ' Expeditions. Transactions of the Zoological Society of London, 12 (Part IV, No. 1), 77 - 141, pls 16 - 27." type="journal article" year="1886">
Norman &amp; Stebbing (
<number box="[821,879,829,853]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1886.0">1886</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName box="[1009,1146,829,853]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malleolus">
<emphasis box="[1009,1146,829,853]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. malleolus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(and 
<taxonomicName box="[1210,1297,829,853]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tudes">
<emphasis box="[1210,1297,829,853]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. tudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), and designated it validly as the type-species, as it meets the requirements of Articles 
<number box="[1005,1062,865,889]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="67.2">67.2</number>
. 
<number box="[1065,1075,865,889]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1.0">1</number>
and 
<number box="[1130,1179,865,889]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="69.1">69.1</number>
of the 
<collectionCode box="[1260,1328,865,889]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">ICZN</collectionCode>
, and then conforms with Articles 
<number box="[414,442,901,925]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="12.0">12</number>
and 
<number box="[496,527,901,925]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="50.0">50</number>
. The type-species of 
<taxonomicName box="[761,880,901,925]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[761,880,901,925]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is thus 
<taxonomicName authority="Norman &amp; Stebbing, 1886" authorityName="Norman &amp; Stebbing" authorityYear="1886" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malleolus">
<emphasis box="[964,1197,901,925]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus malleolus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Norman" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Norman, A. M. &amp; Stebbing, T. R. R. (1886) On the Crustacea Isopoda of the ' Lightning ', ' Porcupine ' and ' Valorous ' Expeditions. Transactions of the Zoological Society of London, 12 (Part IV, No. 1), 77 - 141, pls 16 - 27." type="journal article" year="1886">
Norman &amp; Stebbing, 
<number box="[151,210,937,961]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1886.0">1886</number>
</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
; the authority for 
<taxonomicName box="[411,595,937,961]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tudes">
<emphasis box="[411,595,937,961]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus tudes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is also 
<bibRefCitation author="Norman" box="[680,979,937,961]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Norman, A. M. &amp; Stebbing, T. R. R. (1886) On the Crustacea Isopoda of the ' Lightning ', ' Porcupine ' and ' Valorous ' Expeditions. Transactions of the Zoological Society of London, 12 (Part IV, No. 1), 77 - 141, pls 16 - 27." type="journal article" year="1886">
Norman &amp; Stebbing, 
<number box="[920,979,937,961]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1886.0">1886</number>
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="21.[151,1436,576,1033]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">
Fortuitously, 
<bibRefCitation author="Gutu" box="[348,480,973,997]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Gutu, M. (1980) Pseudosphyrapus, a new genus of a new family (Sphyrapidae) of Monokophora (Crustacea, Tanaidacea). Travaux du Museum d'Histoire naturelle &quot; Grigore Antipa &quot;, 22, 393 - 400." type="journal article" year="1980">
Guţu (
<number box="[420,480,973,997]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="1980.0">1980</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Gutu" box="[492,549,973,997]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" refString="Gutu, M. (2001) Ansphyrapus, a new genus of the family Sphyrapidae (Crustacea: Tanaidacea, Apseudomorpha). Travaux du Museum d'Histoire naturelle &quot; Grigore Antipa &quot;, 43, 79 - 84." type="journal article" year="2001">
<number box="[492,549,973,997]" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" value="2001.0">2001</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) was correct, when splitting 
<taxonomicName box="[876,1074,973,997]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Pseudosphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[876,1074,973,997]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Pseudosphyrapus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1128,1274,973,997]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Ansphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1128,1274,973,997]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Ansphyrapus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(respectively) from 
<taxonomicName box="[212,330,1009,1033]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[212,330,1009,1033]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, in leaving 
<taxonomicName box="[462,599,1009,1033]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="malleolus">
<emphasis box="[462,599,1009,1033]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">S. malleolus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(only) in 
<taxonomicName box="[711,829,1009,1033]" class="Malacostraca" family="Sphyrapodidae" genus="Sphyrapus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Tanaidacea" pageId="21" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[711,829,1009,1033]" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="22">Sphyrapus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
